      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "假设你有几个测量数据点，想知道它们之间的值是多少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "或者你想画一条平滑的曲线通过这些点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22320,
      "text": "插值正是解决这类问题的数学方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "插值是构造一个函数，使它精确通过给定的数据点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "与回归不同，插值曲线必须经过每一个数据点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "最简单的插值是线性插值：用直线连接相邻的点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "但我们通常需要更平滑的曲线，这就需要更高级的方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "lagrange",
      "line_id": "lag-1",
      "filename": "lagrange-lag-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/lagrange-lag-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "拉格朗日插值用一个多项式来通过所有数据点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "lagrange",
      "line_id": "lag-2",
      "filename": "lagrange-lag-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/lagrange-lag-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.36,
      "size": 21744,
      "text": "n个点可以确定一个n-1次多项式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "lagrange",
      "line_id": "lag-3",
      "filename": "lagrange-lag-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/lagrange-lag-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "这个方法简单优雅，但有一个问题：龙格现象。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "lagrange",
      "line_id": "lag-4",
      "filename": "lagrange-lag-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/xiaoxiao/lagrange-lag-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "当点数增多时，多项式在边缘可能会剧烈振荡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "spline",
      "line_id": "spline-1",
